---
title: Creamy Mushroom, Rosemary & Bacon Spaghetti with Cucumber Salad & Parmesan
description: Button mushrooms work a treat with aromatic rosemary and a silky, Parmesan-spiked sauce in this crowd-pleasing pasta dish.
Serve with a sweet and peppery salad to cut the richness and meet your new go-to vegetarian dish.
